            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost">Genio Sanc</supplied>tissimo [<expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan></del>] <lb n="2"/><del rend="erasure"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>S<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>S[<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></del>] </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> ἔνθα κα<supplied reason="lost">τάκιτε <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="2"/>ἡ κοσμ&amp;lt;ι&amp;gt;ο<supplied reason="lost">τάτη κ(αὶ) πενθου</supplied>μέν<supplied reason="lost">η διακό</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied>εσσα<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> κ(αὶ) &amp;lt;ἐ&amp;gt;τε<supplied reason="lost">λεύτη</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">σε δ</supplied>ὲ κ(αὶ) μ<supplied reason="lost">η(νὶ) <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ἡμ(έρᾳ)</supplied> ε ἰνδ<supplied reason="lost">(ικτιῶνος) <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ʹ</supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift besteht aus zwei Fragmenten. Die Maße des kleineren Fragments sind: Höhe: 31; Breite: 14.7; Tiefe: 15.1. Die griechische Inschrift ist deutlich später zu datieren als die lateinische. Sie stammt vermutlich aus dem fünften Jhr. n. Chr.</p>
            </div>
